text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria taitensis is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Kenya.
text.Sources: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Psychotria taitensis". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T32254A9691643. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T32254A9691643.en. Retrieved 16 December 2017.
